{{!
    @template theme_teluai/ai_tools
}}
<section id="ai-tools" class="telu-section">
    <div class="telu-container">
        <div class="telu-section-head">
            <span class="telu-eyebrow">AI tools</span>
            <h2>AI Tools for smarter learning</h2>
            <p>AI membantu proses belajar dan mengajar, dengan output yang tetap perlu ditinjau untuk akurasi akademik.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="telu-flow-grid">
            <article class="telu-flow-card"><h3>Academic Assistant Flow</h3><p>Student Question -> AI Service -> Ollama LLM -> Academic Response</p></article>
            <article class="telu-flow-card"><h3>Material Summarizer Flow</h3><p>Material -> AI Summarization -> Key Points -> Study Guide</p></article>
            <article class="telu-flow-card"><h3>Quiz Generator Flow</h3><p>PDF/PPT/Text -> Content Extraction -> LLM -> Generated Questions -> Lecturer Review -> Moodle Quiz</p></article>
        </div>
        <p class="telu-note">AI output should support learning and must be reviewed by lecturers for academic accuracy.</p>
    </div>
</section>
